reviewText: You should see the first 4, but if you're going to see ANY of Ah! Megami-sama, tapes 4 and 5 (they MUST be played in that order) are it.  I'm very hard to move (Only Miyazaki films and Anne McCaffrey books do well at  it) but this was so sweet I almost cried during parts.  This is an ABSOLUTE  MUST for otaku
